Krad Radio Building Instructions - Last Updated: Nov 10, 2012 - http://kradradio.com

#### GITTING

git clone git://github.com/krad-radio/krad_radio.git

#### BUILDING

Krad Radio uses waf

./waf configure
./waf
sudo ./waf install

#### UPDATING

git pull && ./waf distclean && ./waf configure && ./waf && sudo ./waf install

#### DEPENDENCIES

If on ubuntu do this (if not, you can probably figure it out):

sudo apt-get install libasound2-dev libvorbis-dev freeglut3-dev build-essential autoconf git-core \
libgtk-3-dev libswscale-dev libflac-dev libavutil-dev libjack-jackd2-dev git libopus-dev \
libgl1-mesa-dev libxcb-util0-dev libx11-xcb-dev libxcb1-dev libsamplerate0-dev libsamplerate0 libxml2 \
libjpeg-turbo8-dev libturbojpeg libxcb-image0-dev libtheora-dev libvpx-dev \
yasm build-essential libxmmsclient-dev libtool libxml2-dev 

